<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>网络巡检与配置审计报告</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif; margin: 24px; }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .meta { color: #555; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin-top: 12px; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; vertical-align: top; }
    th { background: #f6f6f6; text-align: left; }
    .ok { color: #0a7; font-weight: 700; }
    .bad { color: #c00; font-weight: 700; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2px 10px; margin: 2px 6px 2px 0; font-size: 12px; color:#333;}
    .muted { color: #666; }
    details { margin-top: 6px; }
    pre { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 10px; overflow-x: auto; }
    a { color: #06c; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>网络巡检与配置审计报告</h1>
  <div class="meta">
    生成时间：{{ run_at }}<br/>
    设备总数：{{ total }}，变更设备：{{ changed }}，未变更设备：{{ total - changed }}
    对比基线：{{ baseline }}<br/>
    对比当前：{{ current }}<br/>

  </div>

  <h2>设备概览</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>设备</th>
        <th>状态</th>
        <th>变更摘要</th>
        <th>风险标签</th>
        <th>Diff 文件</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for d in devices %}
      <tr>
        <td><b>{{ d.name }}</b><br/><span class="muted">{{ d.host }}</span></td>
        <td>
          {% if d.changed %}
            <span class="bad">有变更</span>
          {% else %}
            <span class="ok">无变更</span>
          {% endif %}
        </td>
        <td>
          +新增：{{ d.added }}<br/>
          -删除：{{ d.removed }}
        </td>
        <td>
          {% if d.tags %}
            {% for t in d.tags %}
              <span class="tag">{{ t }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          {% else %}
            <span class="muted">无</span>
          {% endif %}
        </td>
        <td>
          <details>
            <summary>查看变更片段</summary>
            {% if d.snippets %}
            <pre>{{ d.snippets | join('\n') }}</pre>
            {% else %}
            <div class="muted">无</div>
            {% endif %}
          </details>
        </td>
        <td>
          <a href="{{ d.diff_file }}">{{ d.diff_file }}</a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>规则说明（MVP）</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>变更统计基于 unified diff：统计新增行（+）与删除行（-），忽略 diff 头部。</li>
    <li>风险标签为关键词规则，后续可升级为结构化解析与白名单过滤。</li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>
